{"tid":564952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[J到虛脫] 872X頭班車 巴膠瘋搶試車","createTime":"2018-02-18T13:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T15:04:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8e845b414028d18d144d48810922b5949106ee7d","tid":564952,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"新路線872X雖稱是客滿即開，惟該班巴士乘客<span style=\"color: red;\">只有約10名巴士迷</span>，下層更空無乘客。據東網記者觀察，巴士全程約以每小時60公里速度行駛，即使在吐露港公路亦保持該速度，駛至彎位則減慢至約每小時40公里。行車時間約為15分鐘。而首架872X抵達大埔中心總站後，該司機稱巴士會停在總站。<br />\n<br />\n有駕駛872X巴士司機則稱自己為全職，公司亦沒有強迫司機駕駛馬場路線。被問到司機駕駛新路線前有否先訓練及預先駕駛，該司機則回應指「肯定識揸㗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/bkn-20180218184604078-0218_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fbkn-20180218184604078-0218_00822_001.html&d=wKGJgGynjm6lP3PkoXFXvzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2e94ab90\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/bkn-20180218184604078-0218_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb66b91c1bf6155792ff334564a7fa6b8d34b56b","tid":564952,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/photo/bkn-20180218184604078-0218_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180218213445\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180218184604078-0218_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180218213445&h=96f0c604&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"579aec14ab478ccc033bc996c7c58eb99d149d44","tid":564952,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"樓豬J到虛脫？"},{"pid":"b93ac602db60699b1ab7640963b2b430eb0862a3","tid":564952,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"吐公都行60"},{"pid":"14a2995c6ee3d4511a76b7f159f52b07caee8128","tid":564952,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score